@startuml
actor Client

participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "Eureka Server" as EUREKA
participant "Customer Controller" as CTRL
participant "Customer Service (RxJava)" as SVC
participant "MongoDB Reactive Repository" as REPO

Client -> APIGW: POST /api/customers (JSON)

APIGW -> EUREKA: Resolve CUSTOMER-SERVICE
EUREKA --> APIGW: Instance metadata (host:port)

APIGW -> CTRL: Forward request

CTRL -> SVC: createCustomer(customer)

SVC -> REPO: save(customer)
REPO --> SVC: Mono<Customer>

SVC --> CTRL: Single<Customer>

CTRL --> APIGW: HTTP 201 + JSON

APIGW --> Client: Response
@enduml